Standard and Poor's Corp said it raisedto A from BBB-plus the preferred stock of MDU Resources GroupInc.    S and P affirmed the company's A-rated first mortgage bondsand A-minus unsecured industrial revenue bonds. About 300 mlndlrs of debt and preferred were outstanding at December 31,1986.    The rating agency cited recent redemptions that reduced thelayer of preferred in the company's capital structure. S and Pexpects fundamentals to remain strong for electric utility andnatural gas pipeline and distribution units. Reuter&#3;